# Robotics coursework

Pedro, Piyapat, Andrei, Ryan

## Connecting to the robot

### ssh via MAC Address
~dcw/tmp/git-clone-test/raspberry-pi-wifi/ssh-pi 80:1f:02:af:31:19

### scp local_file user@remote_host:remote_file
scp ~/robot/Task01.py pi@129.31.196.157:~/rapp/

scp ~/robot/constants.py ~/robot/robot.py ~/robot/run.py ~/robot/utilities.py ~/robot/encoder.py pi@129.31.196.157:~/rapp/

### mount the pi's home to ~/robot 
sshfs pi@129.31.196.157:/home/pi ~/robot

